/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c1047%2c20220331%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,交簡,1047,20220331,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1047","JDATE":"20220331","JTITLE":"公共危險"}